## 🧪 Testing Requirements

### Functional Testing
1. **Table View**
   - [ ] Bookings load with correct data
   - [ ] Sorting works on all columns
   - [ ] Pagination functions correctly
   - [ ] Filtering applies properly
   - [ ] Search finds relevant results

2. **CRUD Operations**
   - [ ] View booking details opens modal
   - [ ] Edit booking updates data
   - [ ] Status changes work correctly
   - [ ] Delete removes booking
   - [ ] All changes trigger email notifications

3. **Bulk Actions**
   - [ ] Select all/none works
   - [ ] Bulk status updates apply
   - [ ] Bulk email reminders send
   - [ ] Progress feedback shows correctly

4. **Calendar View**
   - [ ] Calendar displays current month
   - [ ] Navigation changes months
   - [ ] Bookings show on correct dates
   - [ ] Clicking booking opens details
   - [ ] Different views (month/week/day) work

5. **Export Functionality**
   - [ ] CSV export downloads correctly
   - [ ] All filtered data included
   - [ ] Proper CSV formatting
   - [ ] Large datasets handled

### Performance Testing
- [ ] Table loads in <2s with 1000+ bookings
- [ ] Search/filter responses in <500ms
- [ ] Calendar view renders smoothly
- [ ] Mobile interactions responsive
- [ ] No memory leaks during navigation

### Accessibility Testing
- [ ] Keyboard navigation through table
- [ ] Screen reader announces selections
- [ ] Focus indicators visible
- [ ] Color contrast compliant
- [ ] ARIA labels for actions

## 🎯 Success Criteria

### Visual Requirements
- [ ] Matches Figma design patterns
- [ ] Consistent with Phase 1 design system
- [ ] Professional table interface
- [ ] Smooth transitions and animations

### Functional Requirements
- [ ] All CRUD operations working
- [ ] Real-time data updates
- [ ] Advanced filtering functional
- [ ] Bulk actions processing correctly
- [ ] Export generating proper files

### Performance Requirements
- [ ] Fast data loading
- [ ] Responsive interactions
- [ ] Efficient pagination
- [ ] Optimized for large datasets

### Integration Requirements
- [ ] Works with existing booking system
- [ ] Maintains all business logic
- [ ] Compatible with email system
- [ ] Preserves data integrity

